                <p> R3-S: In order to better outline what we intend with the &#x201c;transformative&#x201d; approach, we added some sentences related to the Gliessman&#x2019; framework on the food system changes in the Introduction. In the updated version of the manuscript, after the following sentence: &#x201c;
