                <p> </p>
                <p> R1-R: We strongly agree with the reviewer. Often, in European research related to agroecology, researchers have highlighted problems carrying out a truly transdisciplinary approach because it takes time and researchers have to deal with stringent deadlines both during the preparation of the proposal and in its implementation. We believe that an increase of the duration of projects related to agroecology can contribute to overcome this issue.</p>
