                <p> 
                    <italic>&#x201c;In fact, according to the percentages of the ACT categories, in both surveys researchers implementing an approach of re-design of the farm/agroecosystem and the whole agri-food system represent the majority. However, it would be useful to extend the study to evaluate whether those research projects characterized by a trasformative approach were then actually able to have an impact and to make changes in the system beyond their temporal duration."</italic>
